{"about_the_game":"Roboden is a fresh take on the RTS genre: less micro-control tedium with more units!<br><br>I designed this game specifically because of my own lack of competence in high micro-control demanding games.<br><br>In this game, you control the entire colonies instead of individual units. Your control is mostly indirect: you modify the colony's priorities so it behaves according to your plans. You don't order a unit production, you make the colony more likely to produce the unit you want. Collect resources, build and combine new drones, and play with friends in cooperative and competitive modes.<br><br>This game is a rogue-lite asymmetrical strategy game. It's more about finding your favorite combos and sets of options that allow you to perform even better or have more fun. From a chill player perspective, it can be a relaxing game with meditative gameplay, but it can also be a highly competitive game if you try to beat the global high scores!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2416030/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1726011847\" /><br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Split-screen local PvP and co-op multiplayer*<br></li><li> Asymmetrical RTS gameplay<br></li><li> Unique base and units control system<br></li><li> Neat pixel art graphics<br></li><li> Units combining system for higher tier units<br></li><li> About 30 different drones divided into 3 tiers<br></li><li> 5 game modes: blitz, classic, arena, infinite arena, and reverse<br></li><li> 4 biomes: moon, inferno, snowy tundra, and wisp forest<br></li><li> Online leaderboard<br></li><li> Procedural level generation with extensive customization</li></ul><br>(*) The local multiplayer requires at least 1 controller.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Impossibly Difficult","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2416030/29724b979162e9235c40c41bea47b9d032d6456e.jpg"},{"name"